metadata.description:
The "Virtual Visions"- omnichain collection is a series of 2,000 unique and non-fungible tokens (NFTs) that offer an exciting opportunity for collectors and enthusiasts of digital art. 

Holders of these NFTs will have a chance to participate in the free minting of the SkullOclocks collection-Trade to Learn,Play to Earn, which is a unique and innovative project that combines trading, learning, and earning opportunities for its participants. By owning a "Virtual Visions" NFT, holders can unlock the ability to mint a limited number of SkullOclocks NFTs for free, providing an exciting and rewarding experience for collectors.

The project is set to start on May , and all the necessary information about the collection, including how to acquire an NFT, will be available on the official websites(skullOclocks.xyz)
